songs.embed_content: Read “Berlin Wall” by Martin Dupont on Genius
songs.title: Berlin Wall
songs.lyrics:
I feel as if the world
Is falling down
Between my legs
I feel as if could jump
Over the Berlin Wall

I want to fly
Both ways

songs.lyrics:
I don't know
Where to find it

I don't know where to find my "Bonheur"
Jessica and Gemina the vanilla twins?
